snippet.title: A Deep Code Conversation With Jordan Greenhall
snippet.description:
In this video, Jordan and I discuss a wide range of topics pertaining to human communication, evolution, and our capacity to thread the needle of our presently chaotic world and make it to the other side, with civilization intact.

The beginning of the essay mentioned in the first few minutes: https://medium.com/@matthewpirkowski/crypto-beyond-capitalism-the-rise-of-distributed-valerism-7e3c1285a308

Jordan's Bio: https://neurohacker.com/people/jordan-greenhall
Jordan's YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMzT-mdCqoyEv_-YZVtE7MQ

If you enjoyed this content, consider supporting me on Patreon: http://patreon.com/matthewpirkowski
